org.apache.hadoop.resourceestimator.skylinestore.api

Interface SkylineStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HistorySkylineStore, PredictionSkylineStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InMemoryStore

    public interface SkylineStore
extends HistorySkylineStore, PredictionSkylineStore
    SkylineStore is composable interface for storing the history ResourceSkylines of past job runs and the predicted RLESparseResourceAllocation for future execution.
